face="helvetica,arial">
<b>Module Information</b><br/>
Public.USB
<p/>
This is a Pike module that provides an interface to the libusb-1.0 library,<br/>enabling USB device communication from Pike programs.
<p/>


<b>Source Control:</b> <a href="https://hg.sr.ht/~hww3/pike_modules-public_usb">hg</a>


